{"tid":1426071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港特區護照持有人免簽證前往伊朗21日","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:12:05.000Z","uid":57677,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1a55d6d161bc3e6f8905b023ff6c041568fad3b8","tid":1426071,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:38:27.000Z","msg":"香港特區護照持有人免簽證前往伊朗<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  香港特別行政區（香港特區）政府接獲伊朗伊斯蘭共和國政府的正式通知，香港特區護照持有人由即日起可免簽證前往伊朗旅遊，最長可逗留二十一日。<br />\n<br />\n  入境事務處發言人稱：「伊朗是『一帶一路』沿線國家。在『一帶一路』倡議下，此免簽證安排會為香港遊客帶來更大的便利，並有助加強兩地在旅遊、文化和經濟方面的聯繫。」<br />\n<br />\n  連同伊朗在內，已有共一百六十六個國家／地區給予香港特區護照持有人免簽證或落地簽證待遇。詳情請瀏覽以下網頁：<a href=\"http://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/service/travel_document/visa_free_access.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservice%2Ftravel_document%2Fvisa_free_access.html&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=824e3bf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/service/travel_document/visa_free_access.html</a> 或掃描附件。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月2日（星期五）<br />\n香港時間15時16分"},{"pid":"a680c04b6b2777df7d8300d17bdd3257f54d8a3d","tid":1426071,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:38:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/02/P2019080200562.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F02%2FP2019080200562.htm&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=4221d312\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/02/P2019080200562.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4e9def64e1e9655d29d5c1626ed2cddd68d7a19f","tid":1426071,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:39:48.000Z","msg":"去完伊朗仲去唔去到西方國家"},{"pid":"e924c9c5f81b4815da198e1467c330bef643052c","tid":1426071,"uid":151507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:40:20.000Z","msg":"不合作運動&mdash; 每週罷買日<br />\n<a href=